Overall, I couldn't have asked for a better dental experience. I highly recommend their services to anyone in need of dental care.

 Otherwise doctor explains everything well patiently and in detail
reply_text:
As part of a detailed dental consultation ..  It is part of our duty to inform and update our patients about their dental condition.. 

All findings are kept on record. 

All treatment options are shared with patients  .. including pre and post operative pictures and x-rays.. 

Only after an informed consent is taken .. do we proceed to do anything 

Patients are free to take second opinions and come back with any doubts or for any clarifications.  

I assure you that no unnecessary procedures were advised or carried out for you. 

It would be a pleasure to discuss or clarify anything further at your convenience 

Regards.  
Dr Tavleen Kaur.
